⤵️#MobilityMonday ✅Enhancing hip mobility is crucial for everyone. These exercises target flexible adductors, strong hip flexors, and activated abductors, key elements for opening up the hips effectively.

I personally enjoy performing them before my actual workout as it can help prepare my body for it. Dynamic stretches and mobility exercises that target the specific muscles and joints you'll be using in your workout can be beneficial as part of your warm-up routine.
